relevant employees and that of female full-pay relevant employee. 
 
The proportions of male and female full-pay relevant employees in the 
lower, lower middle, upper middle and upper quartile pay bands. 
 
The difference between the mean bonus pay paid to male relevant 
employees and that paid to female relevant employees. 
 
The difference between the median bonus pay paid to male relevant 
employees and that paid to female relevant employees. 
 
The proportions of male and female relevant employees who were 
paid bonus pay during the relevant period. 
 

 

 

 

 

 

